{"tid":1680426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國或禁止受資助電訊商購置華為及中興產品","createTime":"2019-10-28T22:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T09:33:22.000Z","uid":125193,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3728625654a9e14e850d955ea807f7b84efffdd9","tid":1680426,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:38:43.000Z","msg":"有報道指，美國計劃禁止受資助的電訊商，購買中國電訊商華為及中興產品。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述美國政府官員的消息表示，美國聯邦通信委員會計劃在11月投票，將會決定是否將華為及中興標籤為對美國國家安全構成威脅，禁止美國公司利用85億美元的政府項目資金「通用服務基金補貼」，購買這兩家公司的設置或服務。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國聯邦通訊委員會又計劃，要求指定的美國農村電訊營運商，移除或更換華為或中興產品，當局會設立補償計劃，彌補營運商更換設備的成本。報道指，華為及中興有30日可以上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488732-20191029.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488732-20191029.htm&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=88ffccc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488732-20191029.htm&h=171c6169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488732-20191029.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b7e6d0f5a1ef211eef3dd9d2f153797b52166d5d","tid":1680426,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9dfafbfe50943aa384ef26ef90c6d7c55a7f014","tid":1680426,"uid":129848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:45:13.000Z","msg":"中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bf2fcf065a563fa172e001f27076ee3759dbe1","tid":1680426,"uid":281677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:03:18.000Z","msg":"禁佢老味，Chinazi <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9792e5771f971fcd3d37705a1f53b4d22edbc15","tid":1680426,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28